ZELDA VENTER BAZOBUYELA enkantolo ngenyanga ezayo odokotela abafuna ukuthi uMnyango wezeMpilo ugunyaze ukuthi umshanguzo obulala amazenze nezikelemu ezilwaneni, i-Ivermectin ugunyazwe ukuze kwelashwe ngawo iziguli ezineCovid-19. UDkt George Coetzee weSiverton Medical Practitioners, i-AfriForum, nabanye odokotela izolo bafake amaphepha eNkantolo eNkulu yasePretoria, befuna ukuthi uNgqongqoshe wezeMpilo kuleli uDkt Zweli  Zweli Mkhize nesikhungo esigunyaza ukusetshenziswa kwemithi kuleli iSouth African Health Products Regulatory Authority (SAHPRA), bagunyaze ukusetshenziswa kwalawa maphilisi. Labo dokotela bafuna ukuthi umnyango neSAHPRA bagunyaze ngokushesha ukuthi la maphilisi  asetshenziswe nakubantu ukuze odokotela abafuna ukwelapha iziguli ezineCovid-19, bakwazi ukuwasebenzisa. Labo dokotela bathi uma udokotela efuna ukusebenzisa la maphilisi kudingeka agcwalise amafomu achaze ukuthi kungani efuna ukuwasebenzisa, aphinde athole imvume kuSAHPRA ngaphambi kokuwasebenzisa. Bathi lokhu  kuthatha isikhathi eside. Bafuna inkantolo ilumise uhlelo lokuthi bagcwalise amafomu. UMnuz Barend Uys we-AfriForum uthe: “Isikhathi esikuso asifani nesaphambilini. Abantu bafa ubuthaphuthaphu ezikhungweni zezempilo, abasebenzi bezempilo abasazi benzenjani. Usuku ngalunye ludlula nemiphefumulo eminingi.” Uthe i-Ivermectin ibhaliswe yiWorld Health Organisation (WHO), njengamaphilisi aphephile ukuthi angasetshenziswa nasezinganeni. “Ucwaningo olwenziwe e-USA, Argentina, India, Egypt  naseSpain lukhombisa ukuthi i-Ivermectin ingasiza ekwelapheni iCovid-19, okungehlisa isibalo sababulawa yileli gciwane. Yingakho sithathe lesi sinyathelo ngoba siyazi ukuthi la maphilisi ahloliwe kwatholakala ukuthi awayona ingozi." Abafake isicelo enkantolo bathi abalimi yibo abasebenzisa kakhulu i-Ivermectin manje sebebaningi abantu abayisebenzisayo okwenza ukuthi kube nzima ukuyithola emakhemisi ezilwane futhi isiyabiza. Kwamanye amazwe la maphilisi kuvumelekile ukuthi asetshenziswe kubantu, kuleli avumeleke ukuthi asetshenziswe ezilwaneni kuphela. "Iqiniso ukuthi abantu abaningi basebenzisa amaphilisi ezilwane bengenalo ulwazi lokuthi asetshenziswa kanjani, okungaholele ekutheni beqise isikali okuyingozi. Kumele agunyazwe ukuze bawanikezwe odokotela nosokhemisi," kusho u-Uys.